    "Table 1 presents the specific numerical comparison results for different fine-tuning methods.",
    "The results indicate that P-Tuning v2 outperformed LoRA in terms of F1 scores, with improvements of 33.81%",
    "for ROUGE-1, 46.93% for ROUGE-2, 33.53% for ROUGE-L, and 55.09% for BLEU.",
    "The BARTScore value of P-Tuning v2 was also significantly better than that of the LoRA method.",
    "These results have astonished us."
